  tax and before deduction of social security contributions (ECB Staff
  Rules, p.63).   - Do not include investment income or capital gains
  in that total (ECB Staff Rules, p.63).   - Compare the resulting
  gross annual amount to the threshold of EUR 71,764; entitlement to
