  Employment for the duration of the prohibition and while unemployed.
  (ECB Conditions of Employment, p.18)  These benefits include:   - a
  monthly unemployment allowance: 60% of your last basic salary for
  six months, then 30% of your last basic salary for the subsequent
  six months and additional months in relation to years of service and
  age; (ECB Conditions of Employment, p.17)   - household and child
